				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${\rm{DD}}=({{\rm{TOC}}}_{0}-{{\rm{TOC}}}_{{\rm{t}}})/{{\rm{TOC}}}_{0}$$\end{document}where, TOC0 is the initial TOC of the anolyte, and TOCt is the TOC at time t.

